{"tid":2090773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港增9宗輸入個案 10賴死強國人周六隔離完要返杜拜","createTime":"2020-07-02T10:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T10:28:40.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"14022107275282a1df4a6297129898f1dc494897","tid":2090773,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n阿聯酋航空發言人今日（2日）表示，有關該10名滯留香港旅客一事，航空公司得悉香港機場的最新轉機安排，並嚴格遵守相關條例，避免同類事情再次發生。該公司將繼續與機管局及各部門包括民航處、衞生署和入境處等緊密合作，積極處理事件。該批旅客亦將於檢疫隔離完成後，安排送返出發地杜拜。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又指，根據最新服務安排，7月2日至15日期間所有乘搭EK380到港航班的乘客在下機前，必須接受護照及登機證檢查，該航班於香港的轉機服務亦將暫停。有關措施生效期間，所有已預訂乘搭EK380航班由杜拜到港轉機，或終點站並非香港的乘客須聯絡阿聯酋航空或其旅行社重新訂票。<br />\n<br />\n全文:　<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200702/DWVMQCKMNOFM2VO7QSN25P7O3Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0tEuV-VtvKlQ8Oqd6A-LM_f7laMzUyQcNiZ93PI10W7REhAGLPr5lYLCk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200702%2FDWVMQCKMNOFM2VO7QSN25P7O3Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0tEuV-VtvKlQ8Oqd6A-LM_f7laMzUyQcNiZ93PI10W7REhAGLPr5lYLCk&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8MRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=aaf51f7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200702%2FDWVMQCKMNOFM2VO7QSN25P7O3Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0tEuV-VtvKlQ8Oqd6A-LM_f7laMzUyQcNiZ93PI10W7REhAGLPr5lYLCk&h=97b1764f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200702/DWVMQCKMNOFM2VO7QSN25P7O3Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0tEuV-VtvKlQ8Oqd6A-LM_f7laMzUyQcNiZ93PI10W7REhAGLPr5lYLCk</a>"}]}